https://github.com/jvlcode/angular-data-sharing-using-input-output-decorators.git

https://github.com/jvlcode/angular-share-data-using-services.git

Output decorator bayanpaduthi oru event ta generate pannanum athutan customer added appadinu sollra oru event, eppolam customer oda data va inthe event kulla add seirom mo appo la intha 
event aanathu generate seiya padum,appadi generate seiyum pothu,customers appadinu sollra oru array data va athu kondupogum ,data kondupogum intha event ku yaaru listen seirangalo avanga antha data va adanchukulam


Input decorator bayanpaduthi,customers indra oru input ta urvakidurom

@output() customerAdded=new eventEmitter<customer[]>;

emit -- event ta generate panrathukana function

@input() customers :Customer[]=[]
